                        <h4 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-2">Day 1: Connection, Content, & Challenge</h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-700 font-semibold text-lg mb-4">Focus: Breaking the Ice and Collaborative Production</p>
                        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600 list-disc list-inside">
                            <li>**Arrival & Vibe Check:** Check-in, welcome kit, and a casual lunch to meet the cohort.</li>
                            <li>**Vision Boarding:** Set the tone and share your niche, potential, and biggest content achievement.</li>
                            <li>**The Location Reel Challenge:** Teams dive into their first challenge: a 60-second collaborative reel capturing the location's essence and introducing the "COC" concept.</li>
                            <li>**Bonfire Networking:** Themed dinner, followed by a bonfire and fun games (like 'Never Have I Ever') to forge deep, relaxed bonds.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    
                    <div class="border-l-4 border-cyan-500 pl-8 relative">
                        <div class="absolute -left-3 top-0 h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-cyan-500 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm">2</div>
                        <h4 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-2">Day 2: Skill Mastery & The Viral Strategy</h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-700 font-semibold text-lg mb-4">Focus: Peer-to-Peer Learning and High-Impact Content</p>
                        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600 list-disc list-inside">
                            <li>**The Skill-Share Session:** Pair up with a creator from a different niche (e.g., editor + writer) to shoot a high-value "How-To" video, forcing hands-on cross-skill collaboration.</li>
                            <li>**Content Production Block:** Dedicated time with technical crew support (lighting, angles) to film the collaborative content.</li>
                            <li>**The 100K Views Task:** The signature challenge! Teams create a video with a clear strategy for reaching 100,000 views, pushing the limits of their viral knowledge.</li>
                            <li>**Community Feedback Lab:** Present and critique all content and viral ideas. Constructive feedback is mandatory—everyone elevates each other.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    
                    
                    <div class="border-l-4 border-cyan-500 pl-8 relative">
                        <div class="absolute -left-3 top-0 h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-cyan-500 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm">3</div>
                        <h4 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-2">Day 3: Showcase, Graduation, & Next Steps</h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-700 font-semibold text-lg mb-4">Focus: Launching Content and COC Community Onboarding</p>
                        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600 list-disc list-inside">
                            <li>**The Final Showcase:** Present the best-edited final content. The winning team gets a feature on the official COC channel!</li>
                            <li>**Closing Ceremony:** Receive your official COC Certificate to add credibility to your portfolio.</li>
                            <li>**The Path Forward:** Final speech on community steps, future collaborations, and joining the private COC network.</li>
                            <li>**Group Photo & Departure.**</li>
